lead_paragraph: Lagerald Vick scored a career-high 23 points on near-perfect shooting, Svi Mykhailiuk had 14 and fourth-ranked Kansas rolled to a 91-61 victory over Long Beach State on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Vick Leads No. 4 Kansas to 91-61 Rout of Long Beach State
